    "Adapting an LLM for use: Adapting the question-answering pipeline of the LLM to develop a chatbot through fine-tuning and prompt engineering.",
    "Fine-tuning the LLM involves collecting user feedback, and iteratively collecting and integrating user feedback to enhance the model's ability to generate accurate and contextually relevant responses.5.",
    "Implementing the app by deploying it to a cloud service platform: Implementing the chatbot app and utilizing Streamlit for the chat interface.",
    "Utilizing Streamlit, we aim to design a user-friendly chat interface modified to meet diverse user needs and preferences.",
    "Our interface will seamlessly accommodate a wide range of user inputs and responses, by providing a realistic and engaging interaction experience."
